  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, about 2000 GGO patients will be included for a 5-year follow-up. The aim of
      this study is to elucidate the biological nature of pulmonary GGO lesion and provide evidence
      for GGO treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
