    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  35-80 years' old

          -  found pulmonary GGO with chest CT scan and CT follow-up after 3 months shows that the
             GGO remains

          -  Diameter of GGO &gt; 5mm and &lt; 3cm

          -  Solid component of GGO in pulmonary window &lt; 5mm

          -  signed informed consent form

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  receiving immunosuppressor or steriods

          -  receiving chemo- or radio- therapy

          -  can not receive regular follow-up
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
